reviewText: The movie was in HD and I got to see only one disc. The best part was the two girls getting it on.  I would recommend this DVD to my nephew, but until he is 18.

let me start off by saying i like this dvd. I liked the episode back when i could find it free, and decided to buy it now that i cant. which is a big deal for me. now the bad thing is that the bonus content is horrible. its old/poorly done and dum dum-dum-dum DUMB!the trailers are for equally bad/poorly done stuff, but all in all i am happy to have it. second disk though? waste of space.
